title: OpenAI: gpt-4o-realtime-preview-2024-10-01
content: On June 10th, 2025, we notified developers using gpt-4o-realtime-preview-2024-10-01 of its deprecation and removal from the API in three months. SHUTDOWN DATE	MODEL / SYSTEM	RECOMMENDED REPLACEMENT 2025-09-10	gpt-4o-realtime-preview-2024-10-01	gpt-4o-realtime-preview

title: OpenAI to deprecate gpt-4o-audio-preview-2024-10-01
content: OpenAI will deprecate the gpt-4o-audio-preview-2024-10-01 model and replace it with the gpt-4o-audio-preview model. Shutdown date: 2025-09-10.

title: OpenAI to deprecate text-moderation models
content: OpenAI will deprecate the text-moderation-007, text-moderation-stable, and text-moderation-latest models, replacing them with the omni-moderation model. Shutdown date: 2025-10-27.

title: OpenAI to deprecate o1-preview and o1-mini models
content: OpenAI will deprecate the o1-preview model in 3 months and the o1-mini model in 6 months, replacing them with the o3 and o4-mini models respectively. Shutdown dates: 2025-07-28 and 2025-10-27.

title: OpenAI to Deprecate GPT-4.5 Preview
content: OpenAI will be removing the gpt-4.5-preview model from the API, with recommended replacement of gpt-4.1.

title: OpenAI Assistants API v1 Beta Discontinued
content: OpenAI is discontinuing access to the v1 beta of the Assistants API, with v2 beta as the recommended replacement.

title: OpenAI Deprecates Fine-tuning on Babbage-002 and Davinci-002
content: OpenAI will no longer support new fine-tuning training on the babbage-002 and davinci-002 models, with gpt-4o-mini as the recommended replacement.

title: OpenAI to Deprecate GPT-4 Models in June 2025
content: OpenAI will deprecate the GPT-4-32K and GPT-4 Vision Preview models on June 6, 2025. Existing users can continue using these models until then. Recommended replacement is the GPT-4o model.

title: OpenAI Deprecating GPT-3.5 Turbo Models in September 2024
content: OpenAI is deprecating the GPT-3.5-Turbo-0613 and GPT-3.5-Turbo-16k-0613 models on September 13, 2024. Existing users can continue using these models until then. Recommended replacement is the updated GPT-3.5-Turbo model.

title: OpenAI Shutting Down Legacy Fine-Tuning Endpoint in January 2024
content: OpenAI is shutting down the /v1/fine-tunes API and legacy fine-tuned models on January 4, 2024. You must use the new /v1/fine_tuning/jobs endpoint for fine-tuning going forward.

title: OpenAI to retire GPT-3 and text embeddings
content: OpenAI will retire older GPT-3 and GPT-3.5 models on January 4, 2024, as well as their first-generation text embedding models.

title: OpenAI to update chat models in 2024
content: OpenAI will retire three original chat model versions in June 2024, with only existing users able to continue using them after January 10, 2024.

title: OpenAI to retire Codex models on March 23
content: OpenAI will retire the code-davinci-002, code-davinci-001, code-cushman-002, and code-cushman-001 Codex models on March 23, 2023.

title: OpenAI Deprecating Legacy Endpoints
content: OpenAI is deprecating legacy API endpoints /v1/engines, /v1/search, /v1/classifications, and /v1/answers on 2022-12-03. Recommended replacements are provided.
